---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  lang="en"
  active="terms"
  title="Disclaimer | Food Label Detective"
  description="General information limits and user responsibility for Food Label Detective."
  alternateUrl="/app/terms/"
>
  <main class="site-shell policy-hero policy-content">
    <span class="eyebrow">Disclaimer</span>
    <h1>This app is a guide, not a final authority.</h1>
    <p class="lede">Food Label Detective is designed to provide practical and general information about food additives.</p>

    <h2>General information</h2>
    <p>Descriptions, halal status, risk levels, and health notes shown in the app are for general information only. They do not replace product labels, manufacturer statements, official regulations, certification bodies, medical advice, or expert review.</p>

    <h2>OCR and data accuracy</h2>
    <p>Camera or gallery OCR results can be incorrect due to lighting, angle, blur, package reflection, or print quality. Users should manually check the product label before making a final decision.</p>

    <h2>Health and sensitivities</h2>
    <p>For allergies, sensitivities, pregnancy, children’s nutrition, special diets, or medical conditions, users should not rely solely on app information. Qualified health professionals and manufacturer information should be considered.</p>

    <h2>Halal assessment</h2>
    <p>Halal, not-halal, or doubtful labels are based on general source and database classifications. Final religious or certification decisions should be based on reliable certification bodies and qualified expert guidance.</p>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
